title: Ford GT 2016 WEC Silverstone: Qualifying Roundup #FordWEC #6hSilverstone
description:
Saturday 16th April 2016 | Silverstone | World Endurance Championship

See the epic Ford GT make it's European race debut at WEC Silverstone this weekend.  This is a roundup of the qualifying session on the Saturday where the team took 3rd and 4th place (main race is Sunday).

Follow @FordPerformance on Twitter and use #FordWEC and #6hSilverstone to follow the latest action from the weekend.
tags: Ford GT, Silverstone, WEC 2016, World Endurance Championship
